  </item>
  <item rdf:about="2026/0621-sizuoka/">
            <title>2026/06/21: 飯田線の旅 その1 (浜松)</title>
        <link>https://www.don.to/diary/2026/0621-sizuoka/</link>
        <description><![CDATA[<p>飯田線に乗りに行く。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1317" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 11:38:28"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>熱海で乗り換えて浜松へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1320" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 12:55:08"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>梅雨時期なのに富士山が良く見えてる。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1321" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 13:38:10"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>今日は浜松に泊まる。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1326" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 16:30:20"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p><a href="https://travel.rakuten.co.jp/HOTEL/153121/153121.html">今日の宿</a>。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1325" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 16:21:37"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1324" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 16:19:06"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>夕方に友人とさらにその友人とと合流して浜名湖へ。
浜松に来た目的は<a href="https://takiyaryou.jp/">たきや漁</a>。
午後には雨がやんだので漁ができると思っていたんだけど、強風で中止になってしまった。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1330" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:38:28"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1328" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:29:17"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1329" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:30:26"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1332" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:47:44"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<p>しょうがないので近くのお店へ。</p>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1333" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:49:52"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1334" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:50:46"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1335" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:50:52"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1338" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 18:52:09"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>

<pre class="address">
<a href="https://tabelog.com/shizuoka/A2202/A220201/22035960/">弁天島 山本亭</a>
静岡県浜松市中央区舞阪町弁天島3212-3
053-592-1919
</pre>

<p><a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1340" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 19:27:40"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1341" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 19:33:28"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1343" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 19:35:04"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a>
<a href="under.webp" class="image swipe" data-filename="img_1344" data-timestamp="2026-06-21 20:00:35"><img src="/images/under.webp" alt="under" height="900" /></a></p>
]]></description>
        <dc:date>2026-2026-06T00:00:00+09:00</dc:date>

  </item>
